Comment: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:42.86,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The Girl in the Crystal.
Comment: 0,0:22:03.87,0:22:06.06,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouryoukan Academy
Comment: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:10.10,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Library
Comment: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:20.77,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The Girl in the Crystal Palace
Comment: 0,0:23:06.31,0:23:09.82,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who awakened the demon is you.
Comment: 0,0:25:07.73,0:25:09.69,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time
Comment: 0,0:25:07.73,0:25:09.69,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Lonely Pride

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:04.35,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Night suddenly appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:09.00,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Real, yet also not real... just like a parallel dark world in a different space and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:13.26,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black knights attacked the boy and the girl, who had fallen down there, and called them “fragments”.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:15.99,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Why them? What's happening exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:19.36,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Before this nightmare ends, will there be an answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:11.94,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:12.98,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:22.33,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:47.35,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.94,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:52.81,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.11,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:02.66,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:03.66,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:13.42,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What's… that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.93,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.53,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.65,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.03,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Niji High School?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.49,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You guys attend the same school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.46,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No trick there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.29,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.67,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Misuzu Kusakabe,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.05,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Third year at Niji High.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.97,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kakeru Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:03.84,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,She is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.51,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yuka Minase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.47,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,We are both in second year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.56,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.56,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,We are grateful for you helping us back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.02,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.06,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What I did was completely natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.94,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.77,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.36,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.66,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,One thing that I'm sure of is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.74,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,this world was created by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:33.41,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it resembles the real world, it exists in a completely different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.42,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Different dimension?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.21,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought us here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.46,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,to this “Red Night” place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.42,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.34,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bad name for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.05,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.05,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I am not sure of the purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:50.76,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,but, it happened for a reason and we were specifically chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.18,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Chosen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.85,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys must have some kind of power, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.10,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.32,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:02.07,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.62,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.16,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.16,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:16.17,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Tou Sha Kai Jin Retsu Zai Zen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.16,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H414141&}Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.67,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, it's from that place...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:27.34,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a massive aura emanating from that Crystal Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:30.80,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be the center of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.85,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.27,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You two hide somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.52,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:38.44,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, don't go! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.52,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe-senpai, let me come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.23,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll only be a burden to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.90,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:47.20,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.24,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:02.80,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana Dousetsu... Thunder Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.68,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.58,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head to {\i1}that{\i0} place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.75,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.21,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:47.84,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the Red Night ends, you two need to keep on running.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.59,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,When is it gonna end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.18,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, will it even end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:55.14,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it probably won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.52,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It might stay like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:02.65,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's any possibility of a good outcome by going to that tower, then I want to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.82,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.03,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.57,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:13.95,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you run or fight, the outcome is the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.70,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:19.20,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,However I don't know what is in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.87,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that I may not be able to protect you till the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.37,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Still sure you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.67,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.96,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka, you should hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.13,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:27.92,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.18,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, I'll protect you for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.26,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.10,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.11,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:48.61,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.36,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,My eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.66,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you keep up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:57.91,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.81,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you to proceed any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.56,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,So there are some who can talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:26.19,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you are not letting us through,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:29.32,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,that means that you are protecting something important at that place, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.86,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be grateful if you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:41.83,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,She's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:43.29,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,She wastes no energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.04,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,On!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:00.22,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.21,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.83,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:31.17,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.21,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.88,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Lisette.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.63,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:39.47,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been imprisoned here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:42.85,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! Free me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.06,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.98,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the source of the aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:51.86,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,She is probably the one who created this Red Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.19,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Lisette?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:57.07,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Did {\i1}you{\i0} bring us to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:00.82,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:01.83,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.21,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Send us back to our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.67,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.17,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.09,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her subconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.76,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Something inside Lisette,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:23.26,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,like her subconsciousness, probably created this world and brought us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.89,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:26.64,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.35,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.77,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.52,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.27,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:36.11,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You are such a weak man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:40.36,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like the Verard I've heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.81,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:17.78,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,On!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.45,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:25.16,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Your magic is useless in this temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:29.71,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's time for you to vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:35.00,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you or the guardians the masters of this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:38.51,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you fragments are about to disappear, I have no obligation to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.42,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Fragments?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:44.18,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not allowed to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.64,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.18,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Invidia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:52.81,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.15,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.52,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.16,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.20,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:10.62,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Didn't you go home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:16.08,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.59,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.30,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want me to cheer you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.88,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing of that sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:25.26,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you are not at all obedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.92,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you recovered a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.79,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.00,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,How about Minase-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.34,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:05.09,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel as if I am being toyed by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.89,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Happens every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:09.10,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to get chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.72,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:15.02,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned "them", didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:20.98,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there others trapped in the Red Night besides us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:22.65,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:26.53,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Though not many, but there are at least three more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:29.37,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I only caught a glimpse of one of their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:33.41,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I have only seen the other two from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.08,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.87,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of them are from Niji High.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.63,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Two girls and one boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:42.34,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Were they running from those guys too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:45.55,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, they were fighting against the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.51,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.93,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.39,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,In the way of yin and yang,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:52.64,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,all evil existences are called demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:55.73,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from a family of diviners, aren't you, Kusakabe-sempai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:56.85,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.69,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Those weren't shiki,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:04.15,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,which means that they're spiritual beings, rather than demons dwelling in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.99,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps they should be called “Dark Ghosts”.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.86,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Ghosts…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:12.45,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, where did the others go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.33,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:14.66,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I will introduce them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:17.00,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The one whose face I recognized is a third year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.33,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I know her name too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:22.92,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she was fighting, she must have some sort of power, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.46,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Was she a diviner as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.42,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:29.93,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,As for her power, ask the person herself when you meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:36.14,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have some kind of power as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.48,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.02,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, the Black Knight said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.82,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:49.45,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind taking that off and showing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.28,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,My right eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:53.66,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:58.25,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,However, when you were near the Crystal Tower, it hurt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:03.92,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, whenever I've gone to the Red Night, I always felt pain in my right eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.00,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:06.42,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:22.15,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.61,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Minase-kun, you didn't feel anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:26.15,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.11,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.36,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:43.79,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your power is still dormant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:46.17,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although I don't know what kind of power your eye may have,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:49.38,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will do some research on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.76,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have a power too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:54.51,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, then do I have a power as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:58.52,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was chosen, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.19,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I hold you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.15,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:12.15,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to be killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:15.70,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,When I die, stay by my side, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:18.08,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, don't say such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:18.83,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.70,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.75,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.22,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I found Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:41.22,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing with your arms together like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.56,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you romancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.14,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-Tadashi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.02,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.61,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:47.90,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:52.15,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.32,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall over so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:55.57,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hit your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.57,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I hit my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.45,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it possible that you hit your nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.62,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I just did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:02.79,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.33,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.04,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori, help me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:09.04,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:13.13,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like your pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.89,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.60,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.02,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:32.23,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she asked us to show her the new Ayame, we brought her along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.11,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,But she disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:44.25,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori-chan, help me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.83,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I was ignored!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:48.71,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you? We looked everywhere for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.92,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing a cat, and then I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.59,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:55.51,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori, help me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.05,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Two cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:58.47,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:00.76,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to help you, give me 10,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:01.97,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Bridezilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.89,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I would be your bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:06.81,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to be your bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.20,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Today I will take a day off from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:20.07,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go greet my boss, then we can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.03,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.08,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.75,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.80,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you are the new employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:35.92,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:39.97,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Master went out to buy something. He will be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:40.97,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:44.56,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, have we met somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.35,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:48.81,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible. We are from the same school after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.40,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:58.03,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I accidentally cut myself a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.86,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.36,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:02.74,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:09.91,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Yukiko Hirohara from Kouryoukan High, first year, class 1-C.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.67,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me Yuki-pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.63,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-pon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:15.71,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:19.76,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Satsuki-senpai and Minase-senpai, what should I call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:23.35,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,“Satsuki-senpai” is good enough, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:27.10,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not. You make it sound like we're strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.27,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:30.06,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.27,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.65,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.32,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:37.82,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Minase-sempai is Yuka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.94,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,and Satsuki-sempai is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:41.95,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kacchan, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:44.07,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, call me Kakeru-senpai, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.45,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:48.50,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then... Ah right, time for some coffee now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:49.83,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The Yukiko special!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.33,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I invented it recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:53.21,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprisingly, it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.83,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:07.18,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got quite late, from all that time we spent talking to Yukiko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.56,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:10.35,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I called my mom while we were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.19,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming over?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.56,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah no, I will go home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:15.65,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:16.69,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.40,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that we are the only ones suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.57,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:23.07,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.16,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.04,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kukuri-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.50,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,So, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:41.38,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.68,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,If we are taken to the Red Night again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:49.01,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,wait for me here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.14,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:02.15,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:03.36,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:10.99,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm really able to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.00,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:14.37,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.88,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The me right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.91,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:08.26,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:10.39,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:11.85,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:15.31,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You just vanished all of a sudden. I was worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:17.44,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:19.52,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you researching it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:23.94,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can find the answer here, but I just can't stand doing nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:25.24,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:27.45,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:28.45,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:33.49,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:37.00,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:38.67,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:40.25,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,She was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:41.67,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:43.50,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:47.88,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.38,0:22:50.30,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,My eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:51.34,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:28.27,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.20,0:24:40.75,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The black...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.75,0:24:42.37,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.59,0:24:50.01,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: Lonely Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.55,0:24:53.11,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Before this nightmare ends, will there be an answer?
